ockquote>係高登講到我地不值一提，依家見高登人少無人彩你又躝返黎扮無事，真係無恥之極</blockquote><br />\n你食閪屎啦你有廉恥既咩屌你老母\b"},{"pid":"8441f68a01a944b943650e630a306af7c146535a","tid":468714,"uid":85163,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59a804035a545594cc4cf370a9abf2b662fd8f68","tid":468714,"uid":15860,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入你post唔負評，老豆變習近平</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7cd1088924e5882fdd1d139cb22ecb32ecff50","tid":468714,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T18:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1348076e7ce29443ff25624ef03ebd9a17d3e534","tid":468714,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鴻福郎</span>──兩登牆頭草二五仔。連同其低劣笑話，齊名網絡垃圾，人人喊打</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">鴻福郎，於連登開壇時，高調由高登過檔。開post狂刷連登鞋，並大數高登不是，務求用出位言論於新論證博得支持和人氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg&h=9800e8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg&h=8edf56fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來，高登仔揭發連登已成立公司，由商業團體經營，並非大家所想的個人經營。同時，高登管理員為挽回過檔的會員，大量解封違規會員。鴻福郎高調回歸高登並公開道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg&h=74377a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登仔因不齒鴻福郎的牆頭草、唯利是圖的行為，眾人均稱他為「二五仔」，並趕他離開高登。鴻福郎為討好已得罪的高登仔，於高登不停開post攻擊連登，希望為自己的過失洗底。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=091932f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=d194575d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論鴻福郎有多盡力為自己洗底，都撇不掉自己在高登仔心目中的二五仔之名。鴻福郎便盡地一煲，於連登開post狂踩連登，並多番嘗試拉大隊返回高登。此舉與鴻福郎開壇時的行為大相逕庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg&h=ac5575d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg&h=9987c5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔對於鴻福郎的言論行為極度反感，紛紛喝他「過主」，鴻福郎卻繼續以囂張的態度繼續宣揚高登。另一方面，高登仔卻沒有因為鴻福郎的洗底行為而受落，繼續予以排斥。<br />\n<br />\n事隔大半年，兩登分裂已成定局，高登大勢已去。牆頭草鴻福郎後悔最初下錯決定，選了失勢的高登。現在兩邊不是人的他，於連登陰陰地開post發表他的垃圾笑話，希望連登仔能慢慢地習慣他的存在，再次接受他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是，鴻福郎，別妄想啦！人類對討厭的東西是不會善忘的，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過主啦垃圾！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得好，肥絲，我就係最不恥呢條撚屌嘅契弟行為！<br />\n我想問下你，想借用你上而個留言，見條撚屌一次我就引用你呢個留言一次，等人人都知呢條撚樣幾咁無恥同契弟！"},{"pid":"e02b7c2e16929ba959b6600330b58c1fe038fbcb","tid":468714,"uid":102421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:06:56.000Z","msg":"好地地玩fb咪算囉 係都要上返黎柒"},{"pid":"bbb10d2f113e9c03724351bc3e3324080c27ce81","tid":468714,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">难得的好贴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n从顶了这贴后，机不死了，网速快了，电池也耐用了， 流量也无限了，积分也涨了，山寨也变正版了， 感冒也好了，精神也抖擞了，泡妞也顺利了， 查查话费还多出了几百块！顶一顶才一秒钟，真值！"}]}